    <div class="container">
        <h1><img src="logo.png" alt="Subnet API" width="400"></h1>
        <p>Get information on your subnets as JSON with a simple API call.</p>
        <h2>API</h2>
        <code>GET http://subnet.api.hairmare.ch/subnet/{ip}/{prefix-length}</code>
        <h2>Documentation</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="/apis.json">APIs.json: <code>GET http://subnet.api.hairmare.ch/apis.json</code></a></li>
            <li><a href="/swagger.json">Swagger: <code>GET http://subnet.api.hairmare.ch/swagger.json</code></a></li>
        </ul>
        <h2>Examples</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="/subnet/::ffff/8"><code>GET http://subnet.api.hairmare.ch/subnet/::ffff/8</code></a></li>
            <li><a href="/subnet/192.168.0.0/24"><code>GET http://subnet.api.hairmare.ch/subnet/192.168.0.0/24</code></a></li>
        </ul>
        <h2>Contributing</h2>
